sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant AG as Agent (Web)
    participant DP as Dispatcher (Web)
    participant UN as Unit (Mobile)
    participant API as Server :5000<br/>/api/ticket-events/*
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>ticket_events
    participant NATS as NATS Broker

    Note over AG,NATS: 1 — Ticket created by Agent
    AG->>API: POST /agent/create<br/>{ ticket_id, details, location }
    API->>PG: INSERT event_type=creation<br/>ticket_status=created
    API-->>NATS: publish ticket.events.created
    NATS-->>DP: notify new ticket
    API-->>AG: 201 { event_id }

    Note over DP,NATS: 2 — Dispatcher assigns units
    DP->>API: POST /{ticketId}/dispatch<br/>{ unit_ids[], room_details }
    API->>PG: SELECT latest status (fold)
    API->>PG: INSERT event_type=dispatched<br/>ticket_status=on_going
    API-->>NATS: publish ticket.events.dispatched
    loop for each assigned unit
        API-->>NATS: publish ticket.events.unit.{unitId}
    end
    API-->>DP: 200 { event_id }
    NATS-->>UN: inbox push (assigned)

    Note over UN,NATS: 3 — Unit progresses through FSM
    UN->>API: POST /{ticketId}/unit  (assigned→accepted)
    API->>PG: fold → validate FSM → INSERT accepted
    API-->>NATS: publish ticket.events.progress.{ticketId}
    NATS-->>DP: live status update

    UN->>API: POST /{ticketId}/unit  (accepted→en_route)
    API->>PG: INSERT en_route
    API-->>NATS: ticket.events.progress.*

    UN->>API: POST /{ticketId}/unit  (en_route→arrived)
    API->>PG: INSERT arrived
    API-->>NATS: ticket.events.progress.*

    UN->>API: POST /{ticketId}/unit  (arrived→on_action)
    API->>PG: INSERT on_action
    API-->>NATS: ticket.events.progress.*

    UN->>API: POST /{ticketId}/unit  (on_action→completed)
    API->>PG: INSERT completed
    API-->>NATS: ticket.events.progress.*
    NATS-->>DP: ticket closed

    Note over DP,PG: 4 — Reconstruction (any time)
    DP->>API: GET /{ticketId}
    API->>PG: SELECT * FROM ticket_events<br/>WHERE ticket_id=$1 ORDER BY id
    PG-->>API: full event history
    API-->>DP: folded state + timeline

    Note over API,PG: Invalid transitions (e.g. created→arrived)<br/>are rejected with 409 before INSERT
